resources.name: Detailed information on public opinion website

description:
The Flash Eurobarometer 82.2 (step 3) have been conducted between the 03/07/2000 and the 08/08/2000.
The Flash Eurobarometer 82.3 (step 4) have been conducted between the 04/09/2000 and the 11/09/2000.
The Flash Eurobarometer 82.4 (step 5) have been conducted between the 06/11/2000 and the 13/11/2000.

#####The results by volumes are distributed as follows:
* Volume A: Countries
* Volume AA: Groups of countries
* Volume A' (AP): Trends
* Volume AA' (AAP): Trends of groups of countries
* Volume B: EU/socio-demographics
* Volume C: Country/socio-demographics
title: Flash Eurobarometer 82: Euro Introdution attitudes - Flash 82.2:step 3 / Flash 82.3: step 4 / Flash 82.4: step5
name: S1484_82
